## Interaction {.smaller}

 - in R: `y ~ 1 + year + gender + year:gender` 
      - or the short way: `y ~ 1 + year * gender`
  - in eq: $y = \beta_0 + \beta_1x_1 + \beta_2x_2 + \beta_3x_1x_2$


::: {.cell}
::: {.cell-output-display}
